# Risk Treatment Plan

## Objective
To reduce identified information security risks to acceptable levels.

## Sample Risks

| Risk ID | Description | Impact | Likelihood | Treatment |
|--------|------------|--------|-----------|----------|
| R001 | Weak password policy | High | High | Enforce strong password policy |
| R002 | No log monitoring | High | Medium | Implement SIEM (Splunk) |

## Actions
- Apply access control policies
- Enable logging and monitoring
- Conduct user awareness training
